title.rendered: BOSS AIR 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR PX01

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR PX01

Boss Air 12 Volt Air Compressor PX01 available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Small 12v Air compressor.

Oil less compressor can be mounted vertical or horizontal for easy installation

Includes:

  • PX-01 Compressor
  • Duty Cycle 15%@100psi
  • Max working pressure 150psi
  • 1.31cfm
  • Rubberised mounting feet
  • Amp draw Max 12amps
  • Check Valve Installed
  • 1/4″NPT fitting.
  • Air Filter

Mounting sizes are 70mm centres wide and 145mm centres long

To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
